    Lab::new().run(|cx| async {
        scope!(cx, {
            let h = spawn!(scope, "my_task", async { 42 });
            assert_eq!(h.await.unwrap(), 42);
        });
    });
}
```

## Acceptance Criteria

- [ ] spawn!(scope, future) works
- [ ] spawn!(scope, "name", future) works
- [ ] Future is wrapped in async move
